<%= content_for :body_id, "new" %>
<section class="container-fluid">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <h1>New journal entry</h1>
        <%= render "form", entry: @entry %>
        <section>
          <%= link_to "All entries", entries_path, class: "btn j-btn d-inline-block" %>
        </section>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="box">
          <h2>How to start</h2>
          <ol>
            <li>Select the current date and time; this is required</li>
            <li>Tick the optional "Gratitude entry" box to add this entry to your gratitude journal</li>
            <li>New to journaling? More information on the 'FAQs' page</li>
          </ol>
          <p>All entries ask you how you're feeling; this can be how you feel as you write or how you felt at a particular moment. It's optional.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>